<li><a href="http://www.geo.ed.ac.uk/scotgaz/" class="external text" title="http://www.geo.ed.ac.uk/scotgaz/" rel="nofollow">Gazetteer for Scotland</a> - Extensive guide to the places and people of Scotland, by the <a href="/wiki/Royal_Scottish_Geographical_Society" title="Royal Scottish Geographical Society">Royal Scottish Geographical Society</a> and <a href="/wiki/University_of_Edinburgh" title="University of Edinburgh">University of Edinburgh</a></li>
